Package: uppy
Title: Uppy.js File Upload for Shiny
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person(given = "Kyle", family = "Walker", email = "kyle@walker-data.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides modern file upload capabilities for Shiny applications using
    Uppy.js. Supports drag-and-drop, progress tracking, and cloud storage sources
    like Dropbox, Google Drive, and OneDrive via Transloadit Companion.
